narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Altamed Health Services Corp is a Clinic/Center  Federally Qualified Health Center (FQHC) provider based in Huntington Park, CA. From the 2018–2024 period, this provider received $67.6M in Medicaid payments across 618K claims.

narrative.title: Why This Matters
narrative.text: At $67.6M in Medicaid payments, this provider represents significant public healthcare spending. Understanding where these dollars go helps ensure the program serves those who need it most.
